snippet.title: Nick Motil - Butterflies (2010)
snippet.description:
A song off my "Everything's Alright EP"

I think its really cool that there are 2 covers going around out there from some really talented people covering "Butterflies" - I'd love to see more!

Butterflies lyrics: http://nickmotil.com/lyrics-butterflies.html 

Butterflies chord chart: - I'm going to be posting my chord charts and tunings and voicings very soon! we're just trying to find the best format for them to be in :)

tuning: DADGAD

hang tight -
